CHORUS: <i>Moon</i>
SHAGGY: <i>Moon</i>

389
00:23:56.501 --> 00:23:58.492
[RECORD SCRATCHING]

390
00:23:58.741 --> 00:24:00.936
ALL [SINGING]:
<i>Act one, scene new</i>

391
00:24:01.101 --> 00:24:03.490
<i>Act two</i>
<i>Me, you</i>

392
00:24:03.661 --> 00:24:05.572
<i>Let's go</i>
<i>New tune</i>

393
